{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Rancher by day, Vampire by night.</h2>Rancher by day, Vampire by night. Manage your time and resources to restore your sleepy little town to its former glory, all while satisfying your vampire needs for blood. Oversee shops and saloons, farm crops and humans, and explore ancient vampiric ruins in the Weird Wild West!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159260/extras/train.gif?t=1732149283\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Rest here, weary traveller</strong> - As a vampire, you must balance your need for blood with the responsibilities of running a town. You'll want to keep your visitors happy, as they are your primary source of blood.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159260/extras/absorb.gif?t=1732149283\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Craft items to improve your town</strong> - Cater your shops and saloon to different types of visitors' needs and wants. Gather, harvest, and craft your gathered resources into luxury items to make your visitors happy.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159260/extras/saloon.gif?t=1732149283\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Ranching and Farming</strong> - You can have chickens, pigs, and cows on your farm. Pet them, feed them, and they'll take care of you as well! Tend to all sorts of crops that can be used in cooking to entice visitors.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159260/extras/cabbage.gif?t=1732149283\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Cozy Quests</strong> - Don't be a stranger! Get to know the unique characters of your town and take part in their stories and unique questlines. Complete the Vampire Council's mission, and share your vampirism with a select few characters.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159260/extras/friendship.gif?t=1732149283\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Skill Trees</strong> - As you feed on happy visitors, you'll learn new crafting recipes and tech that they know. Each level of Visitor satisfaction unlocks the next set of rewards!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159260/extras/woocutting_3.gif?t=1732149283\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Crimson Gold</strong> - Use the blood essence gathered from your visitors to level up abilities, like transforming into a bat, resisting garlic, and being immune to sunlight!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159260/extras/combat.gif?t=1732149283\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore Vampiric Ruins</strong> - Discover the secrets of your vampire heritage in these ancient ruins located around your town. The ruins are plagued with danger but contain many unique and rare resources.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159260/extras/capybara-ezgif.com-crop.gif?t=1732149283\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>AND So Much More!</strong></li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159260/extras/Building2.gif?t=1732149283\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159260/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732149283","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159260/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732149283","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159260/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732149283","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akama